<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><!--Transformation version 1.3--><legislativeDoc xmlns:xsi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema-instance" xsi:noNamespaceSchemaLocation="http://www.lexisnexis.com/xmlschemas/content/public/legislativedoc/1/" schemaVersion="1.0"><legislativeDocHead><citations><citeForThisResource citeDefinition="#7159#349#000038#     2#         6108#">Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-6108</citeForThisResource></citations><legislativeBodyInfo><jurisdiction><jurisSystem normalizedLongName="Virginia" normalizedShortName="VA"/></jurisdiction></legislativeBodyInfo></legislativeDocHead><legislativeDocBody><statute><level levelType="section"><anchor id="_38.2-6108"/><heading><desig>§ 38.2-6108.</desig><title>Plan dentist contracts; preferred providers; assignment of benefits</title></heading><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_a"/><heading><desig>A.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> Each contract with a plan dentist shall contain the following provisions:</p></bodyText><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_a_1"/><heading><desig>1.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> A hold harmless clause that satisfies the requirements of subdivision C 9 of <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-5805"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-5805">§ 38.2-5805<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#         5805#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation>.</p></bodyText></level><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_a_2"/><heading><desig>2.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> A provision specifying when the contract becomes effective.</p></bodyText></level><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_a_3"/><heading><desig>3.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> A provision specifying the date the contract terminates.</p></bodyText></level><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_a_4"/><heading><desig>4.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> A provision specifying the renewal terms.</p></bodyText></level><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_a_5"/><heading><desig>5.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> Provisions incorporating the rights, remedies and obligations applicable to providers and dental plan organizations set forth in <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-3407.1"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-3407.1">§§ 38.2-3407.1<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#       3407.1#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation>, <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-3407.10"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-3407.10">38.2-3407.10<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#      3407.10#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation>, <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-3407.15"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-3407.15">38.2-3407.15<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#      3407.15#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation>, and <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-5805"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-5805">38.2-5805<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#         5805#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation>.</p></bodyText></level></level><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_b"/><heading><desig>B.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> A dental plan organization that offers or administers a plan under which preferred provider policies or contracts are issued shall comply with the requirements of <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-3407"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-3407">§ 38.2-3407<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#         3407#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation> in contracting with dentists for services in connection with the preferred provider policies or contracts.</p></bodyText></level><level levelType="paragraph"><anchor id="_c"/><heading><desig>C.</desig></heading><bodyText><p> All dental plan organizations shall comply with the provisions of <citation type="statute" normalizedCite="VACODE 38.2-3407.13"><content><span normalizedCite="Va. Code Ann. § 38.2-3407.13">§ 38.2-3407.13<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#7159#349#000038#     2#      3407.13#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation> relating to assignments of benefits by subscribers and enrollees.</p></bodyText></level><history><historyGroup groupType="history-citation"><historyItem><bodyText><p><citation normalizedCite="2004 VA CH 668"><content><span normalizedCite="2004 Va. Ch. 668">2004, c. 668<locator><locatorKey><keyName name="citeReference"/><keyValue value="#1834#131#2004#000668#"/></locatorKey></locator></span></content></citation>.</p></bodyText></historyItem></historyGroup></history></level></statute></legislativeDocBody><metadata><dc:metadata xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><dc:identifier identifierScheme="PGUID">urn:contentItem:5K0Y-PVD0-004G-K3W1-00000-00</dc:identifier><dc:source sourceScheme="productContentSetIdentifier">10816</dc:source><dc:date dateType="last-updated">2016-06-15</dc:date></dc:metadata><publicationInfo><publicationName>CODE OF VIRGINIA </publicationName><copyright>Copyright © 2016  by Matthew Bender &amp; Company, Inc. a member of the LexisNexis Group. All rights reserved</copyright></publicationInfo><hierarchy><hierarchyLevel levelType="title"><heading><desig>TITLE 38.2.</desig><title>INSURANCE</title></heading><hierarchyLevel levelType="chapter"><heading><desig>CHAPTER 61.</desig><title>DENTAL PLAN ORGANIZATIONS</title></heading></hierarchyLevel></hierarchyLevel></hierarchy><classificationGroup classificationScheme="indexing-terms"><classification classificationScheme="legal"><classif